y="honorificSuffix">MD</span></a></span>, <span property="author" typeof="Person" role="listitem"><a href="#con6"><span property="givenName">Claudia</span> <span property="familyName">Varón</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></a></span>, <span property="author" typeof="Person" role="listitem"><a href="#con7"><span property="givenName">Paulina</span> <span property="familyName">Ojeda</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></a></span>, and <span property="author" typeof="Person" role="listitem"><a href="#con8"><span property="givenName">Ana</span> <span property="familyName">Giménez</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></a></span></span></span><a href="#tab-contributors" class="to-authors-affiliations" data-id="article-authors-viewall">Authors Info &amp; Affiliations</a></div><div class="core-self-citation"><div property="isPartOf" typeof="Periodical"><span class="heading">Publication</span>: <span property="name">RadioGraphics</span></div><div class="core-enumeration"><span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationVolume">Volume <span property="volumeNumber">25</span></span><span class="delimiter">, </span><span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationIssue">Number <span property="issueNumber">1</span></span></div><div class="doi"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.251045043" property="sameAs">https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.251045043</a></div></div><div class="core-relations my-3"><div class="relation mb-3"><div class="relation--head"><i class="icon-info"></i><a href="/doi/10.1148/radiographics.25.3.0250878">Correction(s) for this article</a></div></div></div><div class="info-panel"><div class="info-panel__left-content"><div class="info-panel__metrics info-panel__item"></div></div><div class="info-panel__right-content"><div class="info-panel__article_tools info-panel__item">



        
