665">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8316665/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Pulmonary+paragonimiasis%3A+clinical+and+experimental+studies.&amp;publication_year=1993&amp;pages=575&amp;doi=10.1148%2Fradiographics.13.3.8316665&amp;pmid=8316665">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">66.</div><div id="REF66" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Im JG, Chang KH, Reeder MM. <i>Current diagnostic imaging of pulmonary and cerebral paragonimiasis, with pathological correlation.</i> <em>Semin Roentgenol</em> 1997; 32:301-324.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S0037-198X(97)80024-7">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9362099/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Current+diagnostic+imaging+of+pulmonary+and+cerebral+paragonimiasis%2C+with+pathological+correlation.&amp;publication_year=1997&amp;pages=301&amp;doi=10.1016%2FS0037-198X%2897%2980024-7&amp;pmid=9362099">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">67.</div><div id="REF67" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Mukae H, Taniguchi H, Matsumoto N, et al. Clinicoradiologic features of pleuropulmonary <i>Paragonimus westermani</i> on Kyusyu Island, Japan. <em>Chest</em> 2001; 120:514-520.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1378/chest.120.2.514">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11502652/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?